      <title>Fata Morgana: Reflections</title>
      <author> Aliapanacea </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1323022/fata-morgana-reflections/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1323022-fata-morgana-reflections/chapter/1323028/#comments</comments>
