    <item>
      <title>Of ink and Hope</title>
      <author> Silentmass_Louigoas </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1309634/of-ink-and-hope/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1309634-of-ink-and-hope/chapter/1309636/#comments</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">3044700e9a5739a64a79c39732bdf1d0c916d463</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:32:04 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Life is never kind, nor it is cruel. Uncaring and cold? Sure, but life goes on, it always does, with or without you.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is something that Both Iulia and Lu Huan must understand and accept.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Coming from completely different worlds: a grieving sorceress who survived divine war and a dying member of the Blood Demon cult who turned renegade after declining an offer she wasn't supposed to refuse.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;They couldn't be more different, yet by a twist of fate they stumbled on one another in their greatest time of need. For the two need to heal their many wounds: to survive, grow and strive.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;And by this same stroke of luck, the entire world will be overturned:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The heavens will be cast down and trampled, the gods and devils will kneel by will, or by force.&lt;br /&gt; Tyranny will forever cease, for it is the will of The Heavenly Demon and The Arch-Painter.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is a story about healing, moving on from past trauma and suffering. Going from surviving to living and even thriving. To grow and help make the world a better place.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is my first big project, where I am learning as I go. See this as more of a first draft than anything else.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You can expect the following:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;-Lesbian romance starting strong but going into a more slower pace afterwards&lt;br /&gt; -Emotion based ancient magic and classical cultivation with a new twist&lt;br /&gt; -Protagonist strong from the start becoming stronger&lt;br /&gt; -Protagonist who is a fem-presenting trans non-binary&lt;br /&gt; -Intense emotional drama with a focus&lt;br /&gt; -Various PoV changes to flesh out characters and the world around them&lt;br /&gt; -Bad coping mechanism (which will be slowly taken apart and changed for healthier ones)&lt;br /&gt; -Character growth through healing, understanding and empathy&lt;br /&gt; -Depiction of cruelty and child abuse (the chapters in question will be ear-marked in the top notes)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;chapters will be everyday until i am caught up will what's already online on RR, then I will be on a break until christmas, where I will upload every wednesday and sunday.&lt;br /&gt; Chapters will be around 3K to 4k words.&lt;br /&gt; Uploads available on Royalroad and Scribble Hub.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
