      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In a world where magical gemstones grant powerful abilities to their users, the elite use them to maintain the social order. The Leveled system can only be accessed by the rich and royal.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Jacob lives in a small farming village in the countryside, but longs for adventure. After losing his parents in the plague, he works at the local tavern, bussing tables. His best friend, Natasha, whom he secretly pines for, teases him endlessly about his gemstone collection, none of which are worth much, with weak and useless abilities like Half Invisible.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;When he hears of an undiscovered gemstone hiding in a nearby dungeon that grants its user untold power, he can't help but seek it out. Only, what he finds isn't exactly what he expected. The gemstone holds the power to give him all he desires, but in exchange he must give up something he values.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The gemstone takes Jacob's, erm, stones, turning him into Jacinda. As a woman, she discovers there's more to this gemstone than she realizes. It's a sort of puzzle that demands she complete quests before unlocking its full potential. To help her navigate the gemstone, as well as some other new acquisitions, Natasha signs up for Jacinda's adventure.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Together, with the power of the Prosperity gemstone, they will upend the order of their world.&lt;br /&gt; _____________________________&lt;br /&gt; New chapters daily for the most part. Currently on 2 week hiatus, will return December 9.&lt;br /&gt; * before chapter means it contains sexual content (though expect lewd overtones throughout)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
